**** '''Sir Amik Varze:''' Come see me again if you change your mind.
**** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|I go and cower in a corner at the first sign of danger!}}
*** '''Player:''' I go and cower in a corner at the first sign of danger!
*** '''Sir Amik Varze:''' Err....
*** '''Sir Amik Varze:''' Well.
*** '''Sir Amik Varze:''' I... suppose spy work DOES involve a little hiding in corners.
*** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
*** {{topt|Oh. I suppose I'll give it a go then.}}
**** '''Player:''' Oh. I suppose I'll give it a go then.
